{"tid":1477513,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲老婆隔一年懷二胎！ FTISLAND崔敏煥認了：希望大家能祝福","createTime":"2019-08-16T06:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T07:03:48.000Z","uid":123505,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a4e3086a68e54c9123f6481ca6f9ef661d7142","tid":1477513,"uid":123505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.17cloud.cc/images/20190816/20190816134109455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.17cloud.cc%2Fimages%2F20190816%2F20190816134109455.jpg&h=a72e2b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂團FTISLAND鼓手崔敏煥2018年與前女團LABOUM成員金律喜結婚，同年5月生下兒子崔在律，婚姻生活幸福美滿，也透過綜藝節目《做家務的男人們》展現一家和樂融融的氣氛。他16日驚喜在IG上宣布21歲老婆再度懷孕，讓大批粉絲又驚又喜！<br />\n<br />\n夫妻倆相隔一年再傳喜事，敏煥也在IG上宣布老婆再度懷孕，「就這樣，我們又迎來天大的祝福，感到無比激動，希望大家能多多祝福我們的孩子，能健康的出生！謝謝大家的支持。」吸引不少粉絲獻上祝福，表示「恭喜贊兒要有弟弟（妹妹）啦」！<br />\n<br />\n好羨慕敏煥可以日日中出律喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老婆又靚又大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8221386c9c05a6a2a40d21c661e32d1571996fb","tid":1477513,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0WQd7h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0WQd7h.gif&h=2f8b1f58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"324f3a75246ba4b67f470cf37653c68879866760","tid":1477513,"uid":3304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:00:12.000Z","msg":"816遮打花園 817 紅土 818維園 不見不散"},{"pid":"3c6722c5277fc58d934572e6fd261d26d4d0c095","tid":1477513,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:03:48.000Z","msg":"因果由國 容港治己"}]}